Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.80,0:01:59.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,ＮＴ夏利亞．布爾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.00,0:02:03.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在昨天為止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.50,0:02:07.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也是吉翁國領土的所羅門
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.67,0:02:11.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在已是聯邦的佔據地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.08,0:02:16.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因此，聯邦從吉翁中得到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.28,0:02:18.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,強勢的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.19,0:02:21.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在要求援軍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.82,0:02:24.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聯邦再次開始作戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.36,0:02:27.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在想是時間的問題的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.46,0:02:30.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在所羅門發生了奇妙的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.88,0:02:50.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,又再聽到了，是誰？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.48,0:02:52.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,路程是E6
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.09,0:02:54.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,從現場能看見敵人吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.06,0:02:58.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們的整備還未完成呀！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.66,0:03:01.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒可能逃走吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.56,0:03:04.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼了？38區域，38區域
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.50,0:03:05.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,長官！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.23,0:03:37.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,利害的東西呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.93,0:03:42.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那光芒是拉拉所發出的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.74,0:03:44.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也不太相信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.14,0:03:49.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,新類型人的拉拉和MA的艾爾美斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.58,0:03:51.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,竟這麼利害的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.06,0:04:11.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼？是爆炸呀！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.23,0:04:13.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,馬加，敵人在那裡？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.40,0:04:15.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,找不到，那一方的米加粒子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.97,0:04:17.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也很濃的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.21,0:04:20.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼來呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.01,0:04:22.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好像覺得有什麼在叫喚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.11,0:04:25.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,叫大家去作對空防衛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.61,0:04:28.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,米萊，怎麼了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.98,0:04:30.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,身體有不適嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.35,0:04:31.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不！不是那樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.02,0:04:33.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,總覺得有點古怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.52,0:04:35.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在這所羅門的四周，十分的...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.82,0:04:39.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,奇怪？那剛才的東西是感覺到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.53,0:04:41.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,布萊特！         什麼事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.86,0:04:43.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,白色基地在第一戰鬥狀態
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.10,0:04:45.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在等待進港
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.50,0:04:49.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明白了，第一甲板，第二甲板
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.07,0:04:52.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,鋼彈，鋼加農，G戰機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.91,0:04:55.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,出發！進入第一戰鬥配置
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.94,0:04:58.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是隨意的去用人呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.55,0:05:05.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,基加！能拿我的普通製服來嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.05,0:05:08.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,會被山馬路他罵呀！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.06,0:05:11.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒事的，已沒事了呀！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.53,0:05:18.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雪拉，在相信妳的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.70,0:05:20.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在戰鬥中不要帶資料去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.77,0:05:23.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,布萊特，我目前為止的行動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.64,0:05:24.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是假的呀！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.84,0:05:26.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,作為指揮官的去確定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.64,0:05:29.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,相信妳呀！         謝謝！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.44,0:05:31.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,G戰機，可以出發
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.45,0:05:34.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,發生了什麼事？布萊特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.22,0:05:38.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好像雪拉一人在苦惱呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.89,0:05:40.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.95,0:05:42.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,出發了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.46,0:05:46.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,鋼加農出發了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.10,0:05:53.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒辦法嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.67,0:05:57.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原本是吉翁的女人，夏亞的妹妹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.87,0:05:59.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不能被信任是理所當然呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.71,0:06:07.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,又來嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.86,0:06:25.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在叫喚著！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.11,0:06:42.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好像...有什麼在叫喚著！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.68,0:06:48.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼？好像看到了什麼，什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.49,0:07:54.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拉拉，疲倦了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.35,0:07:58.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大佐，沒事的，還可做的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.63,0:08:00.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不！今天停止吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.59,0:08:02.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,成績已上升了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.70,0:08:04.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來休息一次比較好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.73,0:08:05.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是！大佐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.75,0:08:24.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聽不到了，剛才聽到了什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.83,0:08:38.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,的確有什麼在叫喚過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.97,0:08:40.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在這之前的數小時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.97,0:08:44.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,吉翁國，薩比家總帥\N基連‧薩比
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.10,0:08:49.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在接見夏利亞．布爾大尉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.65,0:08:56.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今次你戰端的旗艦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.75,0:08:58.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是不用擔心的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.19,0:09:02.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不是打算去繼持這戰爭多年
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.99,0:09:07.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,總帥你說過用一個月去完結
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.59,0:09:09.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這戰爭，不要說這，夏利亞．布爾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.93,0:09:12.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,坐下來吧！說回主題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.50,0:09:17.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,謝謝！但是，在談那新類型人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.50,0:09:20.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我比起別人更加的去想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.57,0:09:23.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的事，我比你更加清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.61,0:09:28.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,收集了你在木星能源先端
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.62,0:09:30.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,工作的才能數據
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.12,0:09:33.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在佛拿加機關中，已檢討過了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.32,0:09:34.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,放在桌子的上面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.06,0:09:38.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,關於夏利亞．布爾對新類型人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.16,0:09:40.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,的發生形態
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.66,0:09:43.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我有那才能嗎？         沒錯！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.70,0:09:46.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你有自己發覺不到的才能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.67,0:09:51.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,新類型人的未知部份還有很多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.30,0:09:52.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以想你幫忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.27,0:09:56.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今次的對戰，死得太多人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.58,0:09:58.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到基西利亞那裡去嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.08,0:10:02.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不用說也明白了呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.88,0:10:06.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在基西利亞那裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.55,0:10:10.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,準備著適合你屬性的MA
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.56,0:10:12.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明白你所說了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.96,0:10:14.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,準備了送你去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.00,0:10:19.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道為何我要送你去基西利亞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.67,0:10:21.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那裡嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.68,0:10:33.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不明白閣下的深謀遠慮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.88,0:10:37.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是會明白的去努力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.75,0:10:39.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就好了，夏利亞．布爾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.99,0:10:43.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如太過期望別人，會使自己滅亡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.29,0:10:47.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要想我送你去基西利亞那裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.29,0:10:48.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所做的事吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.66,0:11:21.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在這船上，夏利亞．布爾的男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.59,0:11:22.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有來吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.73,0:11:25.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和史魯士中尉一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.23,0:11:26.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,用布拿奧布路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.20,0:11:30.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如那夏利亞．布爾的能力比拉拉更
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.80,0:11:32.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,優秀的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.61,0:11:35.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不交他艾爾美斯的想法是不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.68,0:11:38.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那要點向夏亞大佐好好的傳達
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.01,0:11:40.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,會傳達的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.35,0:11:43.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是木星的男人嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.82,0:11:46.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可能比拉拉更加期待的新類型人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.59,0:11:47.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也不定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.56,0:11:56.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來如此，意外地簡單的操控器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.70,0:11:58.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,史魯士中尉，我何時也可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.77,0:11:59.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,出發吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.37,0:12:02.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明白了，夏利亞．布爾大尉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.10,0:12:35.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.40,0:12:36.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拉拉太過疲倦的原因
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.97,0:12:39.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,技術情報上升太過快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.54,0:12:42.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,使拉拉有了反效果
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.74,0:12:43.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能修好嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.08,0:12:46.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,像今天長距離控制bit
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.21,0:12:48.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,會變得不可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.68,0:12:50.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,比起沒辦法，這方法較好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.52,0:12:54.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如太過遠，很困難的使它回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.45,0:12:56.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如這樣說，就幫到忙了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.59,0:12:59.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,無論怎樣，那精神力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.66,0:13:01.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖能令人洞察力上昇...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.53,0:13:04.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拉拉，可以嗎？      沒事的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.36,0:13:08.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如在等多一會，就可實際的出發
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.73,0:13:11.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拉拉，如在戰場上太過自信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.64,0:13:13.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,會使生命失去呀！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.27,0:13:14.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,布拿布羅能用的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.11,0:13:18.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好！來橋艦吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.18,0:13:25.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,留意夏利亞．布爾那人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.99,0:13:27.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為何？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.22,0:13:30.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不知那人會否想大佐的立場
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.29,0:13:33.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那些事，拉拉不必在意的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.37,0:13:43.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,史魯士中尉和夏利亞．布爾大尉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.40,0:13:44.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在來到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.91,0:13:47.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,辛苦了，我是夏亞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.77,0:13:50.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她是艾爾美斯的駕駛員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.78,0:13:52.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拉拉上尉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.65,0:13:55.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在佛拿加上被稱呼的拉拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.48,0:13:56.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.88,0:13:59.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只是上尉沒有穿上軍服的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.92,0:14:01.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,補給部隊在說的吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.62,0:14:04.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,用那長長拖地的打扮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.52,0:14:06.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在艦中四處走動，好像在煩惱著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.79,0:14:09.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,夏利亞．布爾大尉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.80,0:14:17.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.54,0:14:19.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大佐，這少女...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.47,0:14:22.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不！拉拉上尉好像感覺到什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.54,0:14:25.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好像力量的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.01,0:14:29.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那大尉從我又感覺到什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.65,0:14:32.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不！我喜歡大佐這樣的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.09,0:14:35.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,內心闊大的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.52,0:14:38.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想著對吉翁是很好的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.56,0:14:41.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,受到好好的忠告
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.06,0:14:44.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的朋友，又再增加了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.86,0:14:46.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,多多指教了，大尉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.37,0:14:49.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不！如我們是新類型人的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.90,0:14:52.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了全體的新類型人和平才做的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.54,0:14:56.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了全人類的意思也可吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.38,0:14:59.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拉拉，明白嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.41,0:15:01.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大尉所說的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.08,0:15:03.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.72,0:15:08.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拉拉上尉好像有強大的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.59,0:15:10.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是夏利亞．布爾大尉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.46,0:15:13.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,麻煩的事，好像鋼彈的駕駛員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.99,0:15:15.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿姆羅也是新類型人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.23,0:15:18.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,即是說，聯邦已用了新類型人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.93,0:15:20.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,進行了實戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.23,0:15:22.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有可能的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.57,0:15:24.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,隼人，起來可以嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.07,0:15:26.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起！令你們擔心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.41,0:15:27.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在吵鬥著什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.27,0:15:32.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不！鋼彈的照準鏡好像過熱了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.55,0:15:33.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因此...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.55,0:15:40.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為何只得大尉出發？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.99,0:15:42.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太過正直吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.79,0:15:45.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說過要測試布拿布路也不聽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.06,0:15:47.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.53,0:15:49.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不服嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.10,0:15:54.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我在把艾爾美斯完全調整至適合
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.87,0:15:56.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拉拉為止，不會使拉拉出擊的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.31,0:16:01.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.18,0:16:05.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起！要你特意到來      不
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.12,0:16:11.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在這時候，有什麼事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.28,0:16:13.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想弄清你對我的誤會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.85,0:16:15.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的誤會？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.66,0:16:18.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在生氣吧！我把認識夏亞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.52,0:16:20.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,的事隱藏      是呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.46,0:16:24.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,夏亞是我的哥哥      哥哥？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.16,0:16:28.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是哥哥，那又為何...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.67,0:16:32.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有各種各樣的事情呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.11,0:16:37.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想打算離開本艦嗎？         不！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.81,0:16:40.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那已做不到吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.71,0:16:43.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,已留戀了白色基地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.72,0:16:46.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還有做不來的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.82,0:16:48.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,相信哥哥能做到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.75,0:16:51.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,互相攻擊也可以的說      雪拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.56,0:16:52.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哥哥是不像父母的孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.09,0:16:55.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把爸爸正真的願望去歪曲的接受
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.39,0:16:57.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,自己能做到的說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.86,0:17:00.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是凱斯巴爾哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.47,0:17:03.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,本名嗎？凱斯巴爾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.37,0:17:08.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,凱斯巴爾哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.54,0:17:10.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟著...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.21,0:17:14.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起！布萊特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.51,0:17:18.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是哥哥給我的金塊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.29,0:17:21.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這分給白色基地的大家吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.22,0:17:23.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那樣好了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.59,0:17:25.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我暢快了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.69,0:17:29.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖自己想沒有這樣的戰爭...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.00,0:17:36.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雪拉所選的路也很痛苦呀！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.07,0:17:38.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我打算知道呀！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.54,0:17:41.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明白了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.24,0:17:44.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和以前一樣的去任用妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.48,0:17:47.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,謝謝！布萊特      不！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:49.01,0:17:51.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只是對妳的堅強作出佩服吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.12,0:17:57.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,用頭去想不是快樂的事呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.86,0:18:01.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,期待妳，雪拉，      明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.14,0:18:12.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捕捉到好像是敵方的巡邏機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.51,0:18:14.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,比起所羅門的還急速
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.54,0:18:17.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼東西也由我們來做嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.41,0:18:20.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被信賴的呀！布萊特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.08,0:18:22.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,專門去引誘嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.95,0:18:24.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好！叫各機出發
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.62,0:18:27.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,鋼彈，鋼加農，G戰機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.29,0:18:28.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,緊急出發！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.92,0:18:33.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,隼人，沒事嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.96,0:18:35.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,已沒事了，雪拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.76,0:18:37.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,休息後已好好回復了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.36,0:18:39.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是今天在後方看著吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.23,0:18:40.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在完全回復過來之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.84,0:18:44.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.87,0:18:49.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看到了有三台，不對！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.24,0:18:53.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是拉拉，是別的人呀！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.45,0:18:59.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,夏利亞．布爾大尉，捕捉了敵人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:00.12,0:19:01.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,戰鬥交託你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.02,0:19:05.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我能做到什麼程度，收下數據吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:05.46,0:19:08.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明白了！來了，大尉！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.36,0:19:11.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看見了！一起去做吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.67,0:19:18.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是...很利害！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.44,0:19:22.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,敵人的駕駛員和這邊成一水平線
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.12,0:19:31.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.78,0:19:32.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和剛才不同！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.06,0:19:40.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,下面嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.70,0:19:50.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,鋼彈的反應變得遲純
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.50,0:19:54.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很好的MS和駕駛員呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.24,0:19:57.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那駕駛員沒錯，是新類型人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.61,0:20:00.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如不是，沒可能避開這布拿布路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.01,0:20:02.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,的連繼攻擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.32,0:20:12.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有二，三台的MS嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.06,0:20:17.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,退下吧！這MA和平時的不同
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.60,0:20:18.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,退下呀！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.54,0:20:27.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,加爾！在那裡來的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.44,0:20:30.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,加爾！在那裡？         退下呀！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:31.01,0:20:32.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這敵人不同呀！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.68,0:20:36.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,鋼彈的反應很慢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.52,0:20:42.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那駕駛員，連反方向的攻擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.59,0:20:43.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也能看穿！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.36,0:20:49.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼回事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.03,0:20:51.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,敵人應是只得一台的MA
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:02.34,0:21:03.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,過熱了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:10.85,0:21:12.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,敵人是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:12.72,0:21:15.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼？被發覺了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:17.99,0:21:19.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,史魯士中尉，逃吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:34.81,0:21:36.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,成功了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:37.31,0:21:40.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是太過勉強鋼彈了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:44.75,0:21:48.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,鋼彈的照準計，跟不到我的速度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:50.72,0:21:53.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如再出現剛才的敵人，就不行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:56.60,0:21:58.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,連夏利亞．布爾也被打敗嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:59.10,0:22:00.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如現在立即出動艾爾美斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:01.10,0:22:02.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就能打敗鋼彈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:02.70,0:22:04.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要輕視，拉拉！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:05.00,0:22:07.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如聯邦把新類型人投入實戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:08.17,0:22:11.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,鋼彈以外也...      是嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:12.28,0:22:14.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,戰鬥不可引起危險
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:15.11,0:22:17.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,恐怕，在所羅門的鋼彈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:18.05,0:22:19.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是危險的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:19.92,0:22:23.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還有想想夏利亞．布爾的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:24.62,0:22:26.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他知道自己在基連大人和
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:26.69,0:22:30.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,基西利亞之間，是個不幸的男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:32.06,0:22:35.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算清高地去做，對於他來說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:35.60,0:22:37.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大佐，大佐竟這樣...
